&lt;li&gt;Proof pressure: 1.0MPa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating fluid: air&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This product is not intended for use in potable water systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

